n-attachment-3802265" style="width: 1500px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3802265" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/crowd-Chilean-Couple-Gets-Engaged-on-Stage-with-Paul-McCartney-in-Santiago.-Credit-MPL-Communications_MJ-Kim.jpg" alt="智利夫妇在圣地亚哥与保罗·麦卡特尼在舞台上订婚。图片来源 - MPL Communications/MJ Kim" width="1500" height="980" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/crowd-Chilean-Couple-Gets-Engaged-on-Stage-with-Paul-McCartney-in-Santiago.-Credit-MPL-Communications_MJ-Kim.jpg 1500w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/crowd-Chilean-Couple-Gets-Engaged-on-Stage-with-Paul-McCartney-in-Santiago.-Credit-MPL-Communications_MJ-Kim-400x261.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/crowd-Chilean-Couple-Gets-Engaged-on-Stage-with-Paul-McCartney-in-Santiago.-Credit-MPL-Communications_MJ-Kim-800x523.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/crowd-Chilean-Couple-Gets-Engaged-on-Stage-with-Paul-McCartney-in-Santiago.-Credit-MPL-Communications_MJ-Kim-696x455.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/crowd-Chilean-Couple-Gets-Engaged-on-Stage-with-Paul-McCartney-in-Santiago.-Credit-MPL-Communications_MJ-Kim-1392x909.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/crowd-Chilean-Couple-Gets-Engaged-on-Stage-with-Paul-McCartney-in-Santiago.-Credit-MPL-Communications_MJ-Kim-1068x698.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3802265" class="wp-caption-text">智利夫妇在圣地亚哥与保罗·麦卡特尼在舞台上订婚。图片来源 - MPL Communications/MJ Kim</figcaption></figure><p>这对夫妇来自距离圣地亚哥 400 公里的拉塞雷纳，此前曾出国参加保罗·麦卡特尼的音乐会，并自认为是保罗·麦卡特尼的忠实粉丝。他们计划在麦卡特尼 1970 年的经典歌曲《也许我很惊讶》的曲调中交换誓言。</p><p> “这对我们来说是一个非常特别的时刻，因为多年来我们一直试图见到他，今天就是这一天！我无法用言语来形容这种经历。”阿拉莫说道。</p><p>麦卡特尼目前正在进行他的“Got Back”巡演，该巡演将在未来几周内继续穿越<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-mccartney-adds-brazil-dates-to-south-american-tour-3771223">南美</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-mccartney-announces-2024-uk-and-european-got-back-tour-buy-tickets-3766052">英国和欧洲</a>。本月早些时候，他在乌拉圭站<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-paul-mccartney-perform-the-beatles-now-and-then-live-for-the-first-time-3798925">首次现场</a>表演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队的</a>歌曲《Now And Then》。</p><p> 《Now And Then》<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-beatles-final-song-now-and-then-3529039">于 2023 年 11 月</a>发布，作为利物浦四人组分享的“最后”歌曲。它是<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/the-beatles-now-and-then-final-song-ai-documentary-peter-jackson-music-video-inside-story-3527104">在人工智能技术的帮助下制作的</a>，也是最后一首包含所有成员的曲目：麦卡特尼、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ringo-starr">林戈·斯塔尔</a>以及已故的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/george-harrison">乔治·哈里森</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-lennon">约翰·列侬</a>。</p><p>这位前披头士乐队明星将于今年 12 月返回英国海岸，其中包括在曼彻斯特举行的两场演出和在伦敦举行的两场演出。您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/paul-mccartney-tickets/artist/735610?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=0E63E1ydNxyKT3-2371DTS2BUkCUUnQlnRSW2w0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里购买剩余的门票</a>。</p><h3><strong>保罗·麦卡特尼 2024 年英国和欧洲巡演日期为：</strong></h3><p><strong>十二月</strong><br /><b>04 – 法国巴黎拉德芳斯竞技场<br />05 – 法国巴黎拉德芳斯竞技场<br />09 – 西班牙马德里维辛克中心<br />⁠10 – 西班牙马德里 Wizink 中心<br />14 – Co-op Live，英国曼彻斯特<br />15 – Co-op Live，英国曼彻斯特<br />⁠18 – 英国伦敦 O2<br /> 19 – O2，伦敦，英国</b></p><p>披头士乐队的其他新闻中，一部名为 1964 年的新纪录片将于今年登陆<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/apple-tv">Apple TV+</a> ，以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/new-beatles-documentary-1964-to-commemorate-60-years-since-bands-us-arrival-3796143">庆祝该乐队征服美国 60 周年</a>。</p><p>这对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/couple-gets-engaged-on-stage-with-paul-mccartney-during-his-got-back-tour-chile-stop-3802262">情侣在 Paul McCartney 的“Got Back”巡演智利站期间在舞台上订婚，</a>首先出现在<a hre